{
  "stem": "25348.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I joined the pilgrimage, the procession of people, because in the streets, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] just two days after the-- or a day after the capitulation-- no transport.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was occupied by the Russians, that part, and people were rushing on foot, trying to get to the Western zone to the Americans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had no [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] will to leave, to-- to leave there because I thought that the few times I tried to dispatch a fairly camouflaged car to Poland that someone might be looking for me just there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in the morning-- so I went back to the Moebiuses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I came back, Frau Moebius looked very distraught.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was only after I found her behavior strange that she told me her husband had got home the last week.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He got himself home, and he suffered a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She just got me onto his bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[CRYING] And she said, I told you she would come if they let her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that night, I lost a dear German friend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[CRYING] It might sound strange, to what's happened to my family, to say that, but I'm here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was a friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I attended his funeral.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the most unorthodox things that came to my mind, standing above that plot allotted to Paul Moebius was that my people didn't have a decent funeral.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They have no names-- and no tombs-- no marked names and no tombstones.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was left totally alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know what else you want to know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never wanted to see Lwow, but I did not expect-- somehow, secretly in my mind, I thought, well after all, I survived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Someone must have.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
